                            <item xml:id="a1">
                              <locus target="#135r"/>
                              <desc type="ScribalNoteCompleting"/>
                              <q xml:lang="gez">ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7006Menilek">ዘዳግማዊ፡ ምኒልክ፡</persName> ሥዩመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ ዘኢትዮጵያ፡ ወተጽሕፎቱ፡ እምአመ፡ ነግሠ፡ በ፳ወ፮ ዓመት፡ ወእምድኅረ፡
                               ልደቱ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ <date>በ፲ወ፰፻፹ወ፬ ዓመት፡</date> ስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ለዘአብጽሐነ፡ እስከ፡ ዛቲ፡ ሰዓት። ወላዕሌነ፡ ይኩን፡ ሣህል፡ ወምሕረት፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን። <foreign xml:lang="gez">
                               This is the book of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7006Menilek">Mǝnilǝk the Second</persName>, appointee of God, king of the kings of Ethiopia. And it was written in the 26th
                             year of his ascesion, and in the year <date>1884</date> after the birth of Our Lord Jesus Christ. Glory on God who conveyed us till this hour!Let his grace and mercy be on us forever! Amen.</foreign>
                           </q>
